# v2026.34
#
# User `myuser` is allowed to run *every* command as any user
# without having to supply a password.
#
# Only root may edit this file. It must be `chmod 0440`.
#
# Syntax:
# <user> <host> = ( <user> ) <options>: <commands>
#
# Example:  myuser ALL = (ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
#
# Explanation:
#   * myuser    - the account weâ€™re granting the rights to
#   * ALL       - on all hosts (here only locally)
#   * (ALL)     - may run the command as any user
#   * NOPASSWD: - do not prompt for a password
#   * ALL       - all commands

myuser ALL = (ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
